<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="190" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1437,150,501]" pageId="3" pageNumber="190">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,403,429]" pageId="3" pageNumber="190">Etymology.</emphasis>
This species is dedicated to the memory of Mr. Li-Huo Yao, a butterfly amateur who collected the 
<typeStatus box="[151,249,439,465]" pageId="3" pageNumber="190">holotype</typeStatus>
of this interesting lycaenid butterfly and devoted most of his life to investigating the butterfly fauna of 
<collectingRegion box="[151,333,475,501]" country="China" name="Fujian" pageId="3" pageNumber="190">Fujian Province</collectingRegion>
.
</paragraph>
